{:aiueos.coverage/version 1
 :maturity :m6
 :note "This top-level ladder tracks the capability-decision layer only
        (manifests/policy/broker/graph/audit/execute -- everything
        `verify-command`/`up-command` decide). ADR-0011's PID1-boot +
        VFIO + virtio subsystem is a DIFFERENT surface (native process
        orchestration / real hardware access, not capability decisions)
        that this ladder never covered even before ADR-0011 (ADR-0008's
        retired Rust boot path had no coverage.edn entry either) -- see
        `:subsystems` below for its own, much lower, maturity."
 ;; M0-M6 template borrowed from kotoba-lang/kotoba-lang's docs/lang/coverage.edn.
 :stages
 [{:stage :m0
   :name "constants-and-docs"
