  {:stage :m5
   :name "external-implementation-suite"
   :note "Resolved 2026-07-08 by consolidation rather than by repointing
          a dependency: aiueos-cljc-contract (this repo's former split-
          off identity) and kotoba-lang/aiueos (examples/deployment
          docs) were merged back into this single repo -- the
          `kototama.aiueos-adapter` / io.github.kotoba-lang/aiueos
