          there is only one `aiueos` repo now. kototama's deps.edn was
          repointed at io.github.kotoba-lang/aiueos-cljc-contract in an
          earlier fix, then folded back to io.github.kotoba-lang/aiueos
          (the merged repo) as part of this consolidation; verified via
